## File and Directory Naming

| Content | Convention | Example |
|---------|-----------|---------|
| Utilities / services | `kebab-case.ts` | `user-service.ts`, `email-validator.ts` |
| React components | `PascalCase.tsx` | `UserProfile.tsx`, `OrderSummary.tsx` |
| React hooks | `useKebab-case.ts` | `use-auth.ts` OR `useAuth.ts` (pick one, be consistent) |
| Tests | Mirror source file | `user-service.test.ts`, `UserProfile.test.tsx` |
| Types / interfaces | `kebab-case.types.ts` | `user.types.ts` |
| Constants | `kebab-case.constants.ts` | `api.constants.ts` |
| Index/barrel | `index.ts` | Public API of a module |

- File name should match its **primary export**
- One component / one class per file (except co-located small helpers)

