## Test Naming

```typescript
// Pattern: it('should <expected behavior> when <condition>')
describe('UserService', () => {
  describe('getUserById', () => {
    it('should return the user when a valid id is provided')
    it('should return null when no user matches the id')
    it('should throw NotFoundError when id format is invalid')
  });
});

// ❌
test('user test')
test('test1')
test('works correctly')
```

